query:
INSERT INTO
                scheduler_witness_jobs_fri (
                    l1_batch_number,
                    scheduler_partial_input_blob_url,
                    status,
                    created_at,
                    updated_at
                )
            VALUES
                ($1, '', 'waiting_for_proofs', NOW(), NOW()) ON CONFLICT (l1_batch_number) DO
            UPDATE
            SET
                status = $2
